drop table "CON_ConSignedMgmt" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_ConSignedMgmt" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_ConSignedMgmt"
(
"SignedMgmtID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"PrintTemplateID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"MgmtName" VARCHAR2(100) not null,
"RegisteredAddress" VARCHAR2(500),
"LegalPerson" VARCHAR2(20),
"AccountName" VARCHAR2(200),
"OpenAccountName" VARCHAR2(200),
"OpenAccoun" VARCHAR2(50),
"RentalNum" INTEGER default 0,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_CONSIGNEDMGMT primary key ("SignedMgmtID")
);

comment on column "CON_ConSignedMgmt"."RentalNum" is
'0:没有出租方
大于0:出租方个数';

comment on column "CON_ConSignedMgmt"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
